@startuml
title AI Scan - FE/BE Integration (As-Is)
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam linetype ortho

actor User
participant "Frontend Scanner\nReact" as FE
participant "Backend API\nPOST /api/scans/quick-analyze" as API
participant "Backend Engines\nStandards/Visual/Mock" as Engines
database "Feedback DB\nScanFeedbackEvent" as FB

User -> FE: Upload image / chon profile
FE -> API: quickAnalyzeScan(form-data)
API -> Engines: standards -> visual -> mock fallback
Engines --> API: freshness payload
API --> FE: freshness_level, ai_confidence,\nspoilage_ratio_pct, needs_manual_review

alt quick-analyze loi
  FE -> FE: fallback local TFJS
end

User -> FE: Gui feedback
FE -> API: POST /api/scans/feedback-events
API -> FB: insert feedback event
FB --> API: saved
API --> FE: success

@enduml
